# Cursor project hooks

- **Project hooks are enabled** for session observability (`.cursor/hooks.json`).
- **Global hooks** (`~/.cursor/hooks.json`) run lean-ctx observe/rewrite/redirect.
- All project hooks: `failClosed: false`, `-WindowStyle Hidden`, always exit 0.
- Do **not** re-enable `failClosed: true` or skill-rewriting stop hooks.

See [`.cursor/hooks/README.md`](../../.cursor/hooks/README.md) and [docs/lean-ctx-guide.md](../../docs/lean-ctx-guide.md) §7.
